<!DOCTYPE html>

<head>
  {% include 'partials/head-default.njk' %}
  {% include 'partials/meta-tags-default.njk' %}
</head>

<body class="home">
  <main class="container">
    <header class="banner">
      {% include 'partials/logo.njk' %}
    </header>
    <section class="content">
      <p class="hashtag title-text">#ProtectNHSworkers</p>

      <article class="letter">
        <p>Dear Colleague,</p>
        <p>Will you commit to answering three simple questions every day? If yes, please start now:</p>

        <form name="onboarding-form" id="onboarding-form" action="/.netlify/functions/handle-onboarding">
          <section class="questions">
            <div class="question">
              <img alt="1" src="/img/one.svg"/>
              <fieldset class="radios">
                <legend>
                  I am equipped with adequate PPE, in line with WHO guidelines.
                </legend>
                <input id="question-1-yes" type="radio" value="yes" name="question-1"/>
                <label for="question-1-yes">Yes</label>
                <input id="question-1-no" type="radio" value="no" name="question-1"/>
                <label for="question-1-no">No</label>
              </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
              <img alt="2" src="/img/two.svg"/>
              <fieldset class="radios">
                <legend>
                  I am equipped with adequate PPE, in line with WHO guidelines.
                </legend>
                <input id="question-2-yes" type="radio" value="yes" name="question-2"/>
                <label for="question-2-yes">Yes</label>
                <input id="question-2-no" type="radio" value="no" name="question-2"/>
                <label for="question-2-no">No</label>
              </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div class="question">
              <img alt="3" src="/img/three.svg"/>
              <fieldset class="radios">
                <legend>
                  I am equipped with adequate PPE, in line with WHO guidelines.
                </legend>
                <input id="question-3-yes" type="radio" value="yes" name="question-3"/>
                <label for="question-3-yes">Yes</label>
                <input id="question-3-no" type="radio" value="no" name="question-3"/>
                <label for="question-3-no">No</label>
              </fieldset>
            </div>
          </section>

          <p>Thank you.</p>
          <p>Please give us your mobile number so we can text you these questions every day. Doing this will enable us to lobby the government on behalf of NHS workers everywhere.</p>

          <section class="questions">
          <fieldset class="radios">
            <legend>
              Mobile number</legend>
            <label for="area-code">Area code</label>
            <select id="area-code" name="area-code">
              <option value="+44" selected="selected">+44</option>

              {% for country in countrycodes | orderAscending %}
                <option value="{{country.dial_code}}">{{country.dial_code}}</option>
              {% endfor %}
            </select>
            <label for="phone">Mobile number</label>
            <input name="phone" id="phone" type="number">
          </fieldset>
          </section>

          <p>Finally, please let us know a bit about you, including where you work, so we can perform detailed analysis and see where any gaps are across the NHS.</p>

          <button>Submit</button>
        </form>
      </article>
    </section>
    <footer class="wide theme">
      {% include 'partials/footer.njk' %}
    </footer>
  </main>
  {% include 'partials/global-js.njk' %}
  <script src="/js/onboarding-form.js"></script>
</body>

</html>